parameters:
General Atu: Clea and the others have come too! The current
enemy is a motley crew! Head towards Mount Monimos!
General Atu: Now, let's go all out--

General Atu: What is this... sound... No, is it the voice
of a dragon!?

Imperial Soldier: The enemy's movements have become more
active! It's similar to when we were fighting before... Get
into formation!
Clea: Let's go... We'll charge straight to Mount Monimos!

General Atu: Honestly... What great warriors! It doesn't
matter who can move! We will clear the way! Follow me!
